quran[7{c,v,t}:
59,10,aur ( un ke liye bhi ) jo un ( muhajreen ) ke baad aeye ( aur ) dua karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hamaray aur hamaray bhaiyon ke jo hum se pehlay imaan laaye hain gunah maaf farma aur mominoun ki taraf se hamaray dil mein keena ( o hasad ) nah peda honay day. ae hamaray perwar-digaar to bara shafqat karne wala meharban hai
59,11,kiya tum ne un mnafqon ko nahi dekha jo apne kafir bhaiyon se jo ahal kitaab hain kaha karte hain ke agar tum jala watan kiye gay to hum bhi tumahray sath nikal chalein ge aur tumahray baray mein kabhi kisi ka kaha nah manen ge. aur agar tum se jung hui to tumhari madad karen ge. magar khuda zahir kiye deta hai ke yeh jhutay hain
59,12,agar woh nikalay gay to yeh un ke sath nahi nikleen ge. aur agar un se jung hui to un ki madad nahi karen ge. agar madad karen ge to peeth phair kar bhaag jayen ge. phir un ko ( kahin se bhi ) madad nah miley gi
59,13,( mslmano! ) tumhari Haibat un logon ke dilon mein khuda se bhi barh kar hai. yeh is liye ke yeh samajh nahi rakhtay
59,14,yeh sab jama ho kar bhi tum se ( bilmawajeh ) (amnay samnay ) nahi lar saken ge magar bustiyon ke qlaon mein ( panah le kar ) ya dewaron ki oot mein ( Mastoor ho kar ) un ka aapas mein bara roab hai. tum shayad khayaal karte ho ke yeh ikhatay ( aur aik jaan ) hain magar un ke dil phatay hue hain yeh is liye ke yeh be aqal log hain
59,15,un ka haal un logon ka sa hai jo un se kuch hi peshtar apne kamon ki saza ka maza chakh chuke hain. aur ( abhi ) un ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab ( tayyar ) hai
59,16,mnafqon ki ) misaal shetan ki si hai ke ensaan se kehta raha ke kafir hoja. jab woh kafir hogaya to kehnay laga ke mujhe tujh se kuch sarokaar nahi. mujh ko khuday-e rab alaalmin se dar lagta hai
